data.description: WELCOME to your 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home with a 2 car attached garage on a corner lot in the highly desirable Rancho Sahuarita Community!  Your spacious, open floor plan boasts almost brand new high-grade Italian porcelain tile flooring in main level and bathrooms, brand new interior paint throughout, all new carpet in upstairs living areas, and a recent downstairs bathroom remodel.  Main floor kitchen with large island and breakfast bar look into living area with tons of natural light, and main floor features laundry room and half bath.  All appliances in home stay including gas range, stainless refrigerator, and laundry washing machine.  Upstairs, find your spacious primary bedroom with lovely mountain views, primary bathroom with double sink, large soaking tub/shower combination, and walk-in closet.  Second level also features two additional bedrooms and additional guest bathroom.  Enjoy your low maintenance front and back yards with rock and desert plantings with well-maintained sidewalk and walking paths, conveniently located next to neighborhood community parking area.  This lovely home with newer exterior paint is less than one mile from Rancho Sahuarita Clubhouse, Sahuarita Lake, pool, fitness center, and splash park, and walking distance from shopping centers, schools, parks, playgrounds, and safari trail.  Visit this home today!  It will NOT last long!
